      "text": "នេះគឺជាឆ្កែមួយក្បាលវាមានត្រចៀកធំដែរ។"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage7.png",
      "text": "មានថ្ងៃមួយសំពោចបាននិយាយនឹងឆ្កែថា៖ “តោះទៅធ្វើចំការជាមួយនឹងខ្ញុំ”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage8.png",
      "text": "ឆ្កែនិយាយតបទៅវិញថា៖“មិនទៅទេ”។ សំពោចនិយាយទៀតថា៖ “ម៉េចក៏ឯងខ្ជិលម្ល៉េះអាឆ្កែ?”"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage9.png",
      "text": "សំពោចធ្វើការនៅក្នុងចំការនោះយ៉ាងសកម្ម វាដាំដើមចេកនិងដើមល្ហុងជាច្រើន។"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage10.png",
      "text": "ចំណែកឆ្កែវិញមិនចង់ធ្វើការទេ វាខ្ជិលណាស់ វាគិតតែពីដេកប៉ុណ្ណោះ។"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
