      "text": "វាក្រោកពីដេកទៅឆ្លុះមើលខ្លួនឯងនៅក្នុងទឹកបឹងបានឃើញត្រចៀកខ្លួនឯងធំ។"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage12.png",
      "text": "ដូច្នេះឆ្កែក៏យកខ្សែរចងត្រចៀកខ្លួនឯងទៅខាងក្រោយ។"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage13.png",
      "text": "សំពោចរកមើលមិនឃើញត្រចៀកឆ្កែក៏សួរថា៖ “តើត្រចៀកឯងបាត់ទៅណាហើយ?”"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage14.png",
      "text": "ឆ្កែឆ្លើយវិញថា៖ “ត្រចៀករបស់ខ្ញុំបានកាត់ចេញទៅហើយ”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage15.png",
      "text": "ដូច្នេះសំពោចក៏និយាយទៀតថា៖ “ត្រចៀករបស់ខ្ញុំធំដែរ សូមឯងជួយកាត់ចេញអោយខ្ញុំផង”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage16.png",
      "text": "ឆ្កែឆ្លើយថា៖ “បាទ! មិនអីទេ ចាំខ្ញុំកាត់អោយឯងដែរ”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage17.png",
      "text": "ក្រោយមកសំពោចបានឃើញក្បាលឆ្កែនៅមានត្រចៀកវែងដដែលឆ្កែសើចចំអកអោយសំពោច។ សំពោចក៏រត់ចេញទៅឆ្ងាយ។"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2fd66162f1-827a-4f33-ab61-142e9a97ab40%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a4+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%96%e1%9e%b8%e1%9e%80%2fimage18.png",
      "text": "ហេតុដូចនេះទើបសំពោចមានត្រចៀកតូចមកដល់សព្វថ្ងៃនេះ៕"
